// assume deployed
assume deploy has run

// launch the OMS2 instance
launch the oms2.${oms.env::local} xvm
start the oms app in the oms2.${oms.env::local} xvm
wait until the oms app in the oms2.${oms.env::local} xvm is appstartdone
validate the oms app in the oms2.${oms.env::local} xvm appstate is Started
validate the oms app in the oms2.${oms.env::local} xvm role is Backup
